condition.narrative: The Borrower shall carry out, jointly with the Association, not later than June 30, 2010, a comprehensive midterm review
The Borrower shall enter into a Cofinancing Agreement with the African Wildlife Foundation
The Borrower shall enter into a Cofinancing Agreement with the Peace Park Foundation
The Borrower shall furnish to the Association records and accounts, and the audit of such financial statements
The Borrower shall prepare and Annual Work Program and furnish it to the Association on or about September 30 of each year for a12-month period starting the following January 1
The Borrower shall prepare and furnish to the Association a financial monitoring report
The Borrower shall prepare and furnish to the Association, on or about March 30 of each year, an Annual Report and review it withthe Association by April of each year
The Borrower shall update the Procurement Plan and furnish such update to the Association for approval not later than 12 monthsafter the date of the preceding Procurement Plan
